author: Angela Greene
text: Look I didn't know Taylor Hawkins personally but he was my favorite Foo to watch in music videos. And the only way for me to make sense of this tragedy is to think that God was putting together the most epic band ever and needed a drummer of his magnitude. This world misses you!!
